== Cross-References

@[Equation](label="eq:euler" source="e^{i\pi} + 1 = 0")

Euler's identity @[Ref](label="eq:euler") is one of the most beautiful equations.

@[Theorem](label="thm:fermat" name="Fermat's Last Theorem") {
  There are no positive integers *a*, *b*, *c* that satisfy the equation

  $$
  \displaystyle a^n + b^n = c^n
  $$

  for any integer *n* > 2.
}

Theorem @[Ref](label="thm:fermat") was proven by Andrew Wiles in 1994.

